148
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,319
Aku pernah tak sadarkan diri...

149
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:08,319
RHONDA
GEORGIA, AS

150
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:11,240
saat itu aku lupa soal Lana,

