- Mau mengobrol?
- Ya, tentu.

199
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:34,320
Baiklah.

200
00:10:34,399 --> 00:10:35,360
- Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

201
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,440
- Kau pakai merek itu?
- Ya.

202
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:40,840
Tenangkan detak jantungmu
saat melakukannya.

203
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,799
- Keluarkan kondom ini.
- Ya, keluarkan.

204
