211
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,480
Itu caramu memperoleh
lima sehat empat sempurna.

212
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:11,159
Kira-kira apa rencana makan siang Harry.

213
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:15,159
Aku ingin meyakinkan hatiku
di tempat yang tepat...

214
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:17,080
dengan bercinta.

215
00:11:17,879 --> 00:11:19,840
Ya, possum alfresco.

216
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:26,440
